metadata.name: Platinum Primate #1
metadata.description: Platinum Primates are PFP NFTs brought to you by the team at Platinum Labs. The goal of Primates is to build an ecosystem beneficial to both those who collect, and those who invest within the Web3 space. This will be done by providing utility to holders with the use of both our upcoming $PLTNM token, software access, enhanced alpha, and exploration of gamification, metaverse integration, and so much more!
